If I had to venture a guess WHY you treat self-entitled restaurant owners who are fucking up so poorly, I would say it's because you know how those less fortunate struggle just to make it in life, and see the dedication they are capable of when given a chance, and it well and truly pisses you off when they don't have that same fire inside that both you and the less fortunate seem to.  I have been in the kitchen since I was 4 yrs old and cooking since I was 7.  I have worked in many types of restaurants throughout my life (from fast food to bars, sports bars, proper dining establishments, etc) and have always striven for perfection myself which is why I think I understand you.  Well done sir.  Keep that fire lit... and be well in the new year.
